        "explanation": "Amplitude is $|-3| = 3$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Evaluate $\\cos(\\arcsin(1))$.",
        "options": ["$0$", "$1$", "$-1$", "$\\sqrt{2}/2$"],
