        "explanation": "$\\tan(3\\pi/4) = -1$. $\\arctan(-1) = -\\pi/4$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Simplify $\\sin(x)\\cos(30) + \\cos(x)\\sin(30)$.",
