        "explanation": "$\\sin x(\\sin x - 1) = 0 \\implies \\sin x = 0$ or $\\sin x = 1$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Solve $\\arcsin(2x) = \\pi/6$.",
        "options": ["$0.25$", "$0.5$", "$0.75$", "$1$"],
        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "$2x = \\sin(\\pi/6) = 0.5 \\implies x = 0.25$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Solve $\\cos(2x) = 1$ on $[0, 2\\pi)$.",
