        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "$2x = 0, 2\\pi \\implies x = 0, \\pi$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Find the area of a triangle with $a=5, b=12, c=13$.",
        "options": ["$30$", "$60$", "$15$", "$24$"],
        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "It is a right triangle. $0.5 \\cdot 5 \\cdot 12 = 30$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Find the modulus of $z = 1 - i\\sqrt{3}$.",
        "options": ["$2$", "$4$", "$\\sqrt{10}$", "$\\sqrt{2}$"],
        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "$\\sqrt{1^2 + 3} = 2$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Find $z_1/z_2$ if $z_1 = 8\\text{cis } 50^\\circ$ and $z_2 = 2\\text{cis } 20^\\circ$.",
        "options": ["$4 \\text{ cis } 30^\\circ$", "$4 \\text{ cis } 70^\\circ$", "$16 \\text{ cis } 30^\\circ$", "$16 \\text{ cis } 70^\\circ$"],
        "answer": "A",
        "explanation": "$8/2 = 4$ and $50-20=30$."
      },
      {
        "type": "mcq",
        "question": "Evaluate $(2\\text{cis } 10^\\circ)^3$.",
